Guardian Jobs RSS Reader
========================

POC: basic Ad Server functions
Built on Sinatra 1.2.3 using Libs RSS and open-uri

Currently, deployed on heroku: http://guardjobapp.heroku.com

Items
-----
- take a feed (curr. hard coded)
- render to display as ads

Dependancies
------------
- RSS 2.0
- open-uri
- Sinatra
- haml

Pages
-----
- /sample/[feed] - shows a sample article with ads at the side
- /adbox - shows an ad box 
- /grabad - example page with the adbox 'grabbed' with jquery call


